/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1691882/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T2b0VZQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT2b0VZQ.jpg&h=2ac5df0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原來係連登x蘋果吹雞<br />\n難怪有哂地點時間表<br />\n鑊鑊都港島，鑊鑊都推人去死<br />\n流人哋嘅血成就自己得票當選！<br />\n泛民蘋果全部都要仆街冚家鏟！<br />\n<br />\n好彩我一早就同班泛民左膠割晒蓆姐，分化實在好！<img src=\"http://lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n快d回&quot;拉，不分化，不推文回覆啦&quot;<img src=\"http://lihkg.com/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<code>#1 - 香港既和理非從來唔保護勇武，甚至會阻止勇武制服勇武出賣勇武，所以和理非實則係港奸</code><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1661812/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1661812/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<blockquote>泛民港奸！<img src=\"http://lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"c7d5af862bcd0cfb4a7f7a656586c6ae1ea5bd64","tid":1739793,"uid":25468,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T17:27:42.000Z","msg":"每個逃生方法理論上只能用一次 , 第二次已經要假設已被發現"},{"pid":"19e3a26416bb0023d58dc95be89a6340ee253e1f","tid":1739793,"uid":65686,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T17:29:09.000Z","msg":"五毛來，大家可以block"},{"pid":"a1681fc716f604f053b906d2a38c5f8a8ad3453b","tid":1739793,"uid":4599,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T17:29:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你咪on9啦⋯黃咗先出報道㗎on9仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"3f2a2c280ee53cc4eb4bbdcac27cbbc4cde2d125","tid":1739793,"uid":310914,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T17:31:30.000Z","msg":"蘋果日報唔係第一次篤灰￼，之前有影手足嘅大頭相￼"},{"pid":"0982156fb391f0ac6c6a85c8092b70bf6eb16fd3","tid":1739793,"uid":338636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"